---
// Footer Organism
---
<footer class="bg-principal text-slate-200 border-t-8 border-destaque mt-16 md:mt-32 relative z-20">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-12 md:py-16 max-w-7xl">
        <div class="footer flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between gap-10">
            <aside class="flex flex-col gap-6 max-w-sm">
                <h3 class="font-heading font-black text-5xl text-destaque uppercase tracking-tighter">Inst. Hub</h3>
                <p class="text-xl font-medium border-l-4 border-destaque pl-4">
                    Instituto de Religião de Porto Alegre.<br/>
                    Conectando jovens adultos com propósito.
                </p>
            </aside> 
            <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-12 md:gap-20">
                <nav class="flex flex-col gap-4">
                    <h6 class="footer-title text-destaque font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-lg opacity-100">Navegação</h6> 
                    <a href="/" class="link link-hover text-lg font-medium hover:text-destaque transition-colors">Início</a>
                    <a href="/aulas" class="link link-hover text-lg font-medium hover:text-destaque transition-colors">Grade de Aulas</a>
                    <a href="/cronograma" class="link link-hover text-lg font-medium hover:text-destaque transition-colors">Cronograma & Eventos</a>
                    <a href="/sobre" class="link link-hover text-lg font-medium hover:text-destaque transition-colors">Sobre o Instituto</a>
                </nav> 
                <nav class="flex flex-col gap-4">
                    <h6 class="footer-title text-destaque font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-lg opacity-100">Redes Sociais</h6> 
                    <a href="https://www.instagram.com/institutopoa/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" aria-label="Acessar Instagram do Instituto" class="link link-hover text-lg font-medium hover:text-destaque transition-colors flex items-center gap-2">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="2" y="2" width="20" height="20" rx="5" ry="5"></rect><path d="M16 11.37A4 4 0 1 1 12.63 8 4 4 0 0 1 16 11.37z"></path><line x1="17.5" y1="6.5" x2="17.51" y2="6.5"></line></svg>
                        Instagram
                    </a>
                </nav>
                <nav class="flex flex-col gap-4">
                    <h6 class="footer-title text-destaque font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-lg opacity-100">Horários de funcionamento</h6> 
                    <div class="text-lg font-medium leading-tight">
                        <p class="mb-2">
                            <span class="text-destaque block text-sm uppercase tracking-wider font-bold">Seg, Ter e Sáb</span>
                            8h às 17h
                        </p>
                        <p>
                            <span class="text-destaque block text-sm uppercase tracking-wider font-bold">Qua e Qui</span>
                            14h às 22h
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </nav>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-16 pt-8 border-t-4 border-principal/50 flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center gap-4 text-blue-200 font-medium">
            <p>&copy; 2026 Instituto Hub. Todos os direitos reservados.</p>
            <p class="font-bold flex items-center gap-1">Feito com <span class="text-destaque text-xl">🚀</span> no RS</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</footer>
